1048.name: AA NiCro 600
1048.Applications: AA NICRO 600 is developed for welding and cladding nickel-based alloys such as alloy 600 or similar materials. This alloy can also be used for welding dissimilar nickel-based alloys to each other, to alloyed steels or to stainless steels. AA NICRO 600 can also be used on difficult to weld steels !
1048.Suitable_For: Alloy type : Incoloy 800, DS - Inconel 600, 601, UNS Nr (unified numbering system) : K 81340, N06600, N 06601, N 08800, N 08810.
